      "index": 2,
      "text": "…My Lord Karosas. My forces have just liberated your system from Directorate control. At this time yesterday afternoon, I was <i>waging war</i> on your behalf.\n\nAs your liege lady, I <i>require</i> your loyalty and the aid of your technologists. And I <i>expect</i> you to provide it.",
      "branches": [
