    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ce95c0dcf921ff89c1e6c4c"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "And where were you while your sworn allies were under attack? While your people were being <i>slaughtered</i>?! You were <i>hiding on the damned Frontier</i>.\n\nI saw your little broadcast from Weldry. By your own admission, you <i>left us to die</i>!",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "[Say nothing.]",
          "conditions": null,
