        "id": "9c0ed5e7b2ae2c781d7269d0"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "We understand the hardships that you have suffered, sir. But from this point forward, you will show me the respect that I am due.\n\n<i>Your own son</i> was released from captivity by <i>my</i> hand. I <i>fought and bled</i> to set him free.",
