      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ccdfdba2b87ba496410b2f2"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "You saved my Otto, yes. But he isn't the man I remember anymore. The prison administrators on Weldry <i>did something</i> to his mind.\n\nAnd my daughter, Lina…",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
