      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c6af13e441e0f6e59584ef2"
      },
      "index": 7,
      "text": "She supported you, you know. Even after you abandoned us to our fate, she refused to break faith with you.\n\nShe sang your praises to all who would listen… until the Directorate made an example of her.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
