      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c54217acb2cbf104abcb77c"
      },
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Lina was barely twenty years old when she died in your name. My fealty to your cause died with her. And so, if you want my help, you will <i>compensate</i> me for it.\n\nYou have a job for my technologists, and I have a job for your mercenaries. We'll trade service for service, or you'll leave here with nothing.",
      "branches": [
